---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import styles from '../styles/support.module.css';
---

<Layout title="Support - Shimmr" description="Get help and support for Shimmr app.">
  <div class={styles.supportContainer}>
    <div class={styles.content}>
      <h2 class={styles.sectionHeading}>Customer Support</h2>
      <p>
        Welcome to Shimmr's support page. We're here to help you get the most out of your sound
        therapy experience. If you have any questions, feedback, or need assistance with the app,
        our team is ready to help.
      </p>

      <h2 class={styles.sectionHeading}>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        The easiest way to reach us is via email. We aim to respond to all inquiries within 24-48
        hours during business days.
      </p>
      <p>
        Email us at: <a href="mailto:hi@shimmr.app" class={styles.emailLink}>hi@shimmr.app</a>
      </p>

      <h2 class={styles.sectionHeading}>Download Shimmr</h2>
      <p>Get the latest version of Shimmr from the App Store:</p>
      <div class={styles.appStoreLink}>
        <a
          href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/shimmr-meditation-sleep/id6479964631?itscg=30200&itsct=apps_box_badge&mttnsubad=6479964631"
          aria-label="Download on the App Store"
        >
          <img
            src="https://toolbox.marketingtools.apple.com/api/v2/badges/download-on-the-app-store/black/en-us?releaseDate=1721865600"
            alt="Download on the App Store"
          />
        </a>
      </div>

      <h2 class={styles.sectionHeading}>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p>
        We're working on a comprehensive FAQ section. In the meantime, please don't hesitate to
        reach out with any questions you might have about Shimmr.
      </p>

      <h2 class={styles.sectionHeading}>Legal Information</h2>
      <p>
        For information about how we handle your data and the terms of using our service, please
        refer to our legal documents:
      </p>

      <div class={styles.legalLinks}>
        <a href="/legal/privacy-policy" class={styles.legalLink}>Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="/legal/terms-of-service" class={styles.legalLink}>Terms of Service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
